{"tid":1386051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"野貓式堵路 打遊擊先係出路！！！","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:44:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T13:16:09.000Z","uid":67645,"like":313,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"b50d3163ef64c7ee864911da6bc01328fe4895b3","tid":1386051,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:44:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">728 49位手足被捕 總共182位被捕</span></span><br />\n上過前線相信明白 我地同班狗之間裝備實力差距有幾大<br />\n人地就拎長盾開槍射鳩你 手足拎住個爛鳩紙皮盾 雪榚筒<br />\n人地射粒催淚彈 前線未退 後面嘅已經唔見哂<br />\n琴日發夢見到速龍兩條街一齊夾過黎 幾個手足係身邊已經比人㩒低左<br />\n宜家仲要出水炮車 硬碰絕對係零贏面<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我係垃圾 我諗返起差少少就比人㩒低就訓唔到</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我唔係要怪無人救人或者大家淨係識退<br />\n但係我地要諗辦法降低傷亡</span></span><br />\n<br />\n琴日大家有無諗過係西環對抗有咩目的？<br />\n有人覺得真係攻到入去中聯辦？<br />\n我會跟住上前線係因為知道有手足係前線唔夠支援，要人上去幫手，唔想有手足被捉。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但係一開始目的係咩？</span></span><br />\n大家知佔領死守一定輸 點解係到要企定定比人射？<br />\n目的係要增加管治成本 令到班狗消耗體力更加唔可以守住同一個地方！！！<br />\n佢地就企定定開槍 輪住企前面玩槍射鳩你<br />\n我地就水都唔敢飲 怕一除豬咀就奶野<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">麻煩起好路障就轉地方！</span></span><br />\n發過咁多次夢都知 狗係唔會一起完就衝過黎拆<br />\n轉地方後，佢地又要重新部署，部署完我地又可以轉地方<br />\n咁樣玩法唔好講水炮車，催淚佢都唔知應該點放好！<br />\n<br />\n好似琴日銅鑼灣，班狗完全無佈防，應該好好擴大優勢唔係坐係度，然後見無野做就過去支援西環！<br />\n全部人係哂西環，班狗只需要係重兵西環就搞掂！<br />\n如果當時可以搞到多個不同地區都交通受阻，班狗仲能唔能夠冷處理？<br />\nBe water唔係口號，唔係叫人撒退！<br />\n進攻都應該Be water，減少手足傷亡被捕，發揮最大抗爭成果！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ab241045c6c10ca260b34b8759e0be66c976ff20","tid":1386051,"uid":1392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:45:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n夢想做工程師或者汽車維修員既同學仔入一入黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1383220\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1383220</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幫手推"},{"pid":"e4ffdf933291c1af152e84952ccf66007eee035b","tid":1386051,"uid":282624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:45:02.000Z","msg":"光復香港"},{"pid":"1beaa19959f5f1565fa0ed82845ef3e4071264ff","tid":1386051,"uid":4496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa2a2a32edba4ef6b1ac64f1a9828b21b95dcdf4","tid":1386051,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:45:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"c486e7aac297e9aa0277fd68d96ddf6cf4a375d9","tid":1386051,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:47:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0dadee2473ea721cd2463bc7404c625db591c57a","tid":1386051,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:48:38.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"665bedb795b631b12ab29080c8619bab9649ba4d","tid":1386051,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:49:39.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"fd19183e6470d34140da0f0a5bf5db14f4035194","tid":1386051,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:50:09.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"444e4f4fb00a76924e46fbf919bdcca040eabdec","tid":1386051,"uid":67645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:50:43.000Z","msg":"光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"56395fd4353dca032be603fadad53a294f61413e","tid