yTime":"2019-07-30T14:11:19.000Z","msg":"見到隔籬post有講<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:33:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1370a78f375beb3f6768da4747555e3613d545bb","tid":1386051,"uid":260077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"講就易既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33cf2b380227a7e828a8b1fe040ec8ebefa0dc4f","tid":1386051,"uid":281486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"其實真係要轉打游擊先夠玩。<br />\n因為拉下又一個，拉下又一個，淨返唔多前線架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273163b55a256c6a6e8a5f5928ad7cd14d7b5705","tid":1386051,"uid":57088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"13e34e93e9f8446e8501a48e99f613fbfd95a5b1","tid":1386051,"uid":263806,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T14:58:56.000Z","msg":"▇▇ 要贏就要影響到全香港 ▇▇<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1387054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1387054</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bc813152406b6017f2b93789a37d7e593d376035","tid":1386051,"uid":231594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:00:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"459283675ac2df0fc5baf990eccfaa237519d3ff","tid":1386051,"uid":281606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:47:54.000Z","msg":"推戰術po"},{"pid":"d33be1dc56af13c57aacf64d250b4c6d3c6d1935","tid":1386051,"uid":260367,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T16:02: